TR.PULSE 1-4
	interaction with manual set high/low?


(((pattern funcs))) N = four possible patterns

 P I (X)			ignores LENGTH

 P.INSERT I X	insert X at position I (increases LENGTH)
 P.DELETE I 		delete at specified I (decreases LENGTH)

 P.PUSH X 		add X to end (with respect to LENGTH)
 P.POP			return/remove last element

 (add/remove just use p.insert p.i )

get/set VAR

 P.N 			N pattern to work with

 P.LENGTH 		manually change length. non-destructive.

 P.I 			INDEX
 P.WRAP
 P.START
 P.END
 P.HERE
 P.NEXT
 P.PREV


 PN n i (x)


